# GitHub Actions — iOS (this repository)

Canonical paths are under **`.github/workflows/`**.

## Orchestrator — `.github/workflows/ios.yml`

- **Triggers**: `push` / `pull_request` to **`main`** and **`master`**; **`workflow_dispatch`** (optional “upload to TestFlight” for the archive path).
- **DAG** (reusable `workflow_call` jobs):

| Job | Workflow file |
|-----|----------------|
| Lint (SwiftLint + SwiftFormat) | `ios-job-lint.yml` |
| Security (Semgrep, TruffleHog, Snyk) | `ios-job-security.yml` |
| Simulator Debug `.app` artifact | `ios-job-simulator-artifact.yml` |
| Unit tests + **xccov** line coverage gate | `ios-job-test.yml` |
| Match + `gym` IPA (push to `main`/`master` or manual dispatch) | `ios-release.yml` |

- **Runner / Xcode**: `macos-15` + **`maxim-lobanov/setup-xcode@v1`** with **`env.XCODE_VERSION: latest-stable`** (set in each reusable workflow; keep them aligned when you switch to a pin).
- **Project**: **`PipelineGeneric/PipelineGeneric.xcodeproj`**, scheme **`PipelineGeneric`**, bundle id **`com.codeandtheory.PipelineGeneric`**.

## Simulator artifact — `.github/workflows/ios-job-simulator-artifact.yml`

- **`xcodebuild build`** (not `test`) on an available iPhone Simulator destination (`platform=…,name=…,OS=…`) from **`.github/scripts/ios_first_iphone_sim_udid.py`**.
- **Unsigned**: `CODE_SIGNING_ALLOWED=NO`, `DerivedDataPath` **`DerivedDataCI`**.
- **Artifact**: `DerivedDataCI/Build/Products/Debug-iphonesimulator/PipelineGeneric.app` (name/input may use scheme).

## Tests & coverage — `.github/workflows/ios-job-test.yml`

- **`xcodebuild test`** with **`-enableCodeCoverage YES`**, `TestResults.xcresult`, then **`xcrun xccov view --report --json`** + Python gate vs **`coverage_threshold_percent`** (default **80**).
- **Destination**: **`simulator_destination`** defaults to **`auto`** (empty also treated as auto) → **`-destination`** string via **`.github/scripts/ios_first_iphone_sim_udid.py`** (`platform=iOS Simulator,name=…,OS=…`). Use any other value as the full **`-destination`** string to pin a simulator (avoid stale **`id=`** UDIDs from another Mac).

## Archive / TestFlight — `.github/workflows/ios-release.yml` + **`fastlane/Fastfile`**

- **Signing**: **Fastlane Match** (read-only app store), not base64 `.p12` / profile in YAML.
- **Secrets**: `APP_STORE_CONNECT_*`, `MATCH_PASSWORD`, `MATCH_GIT_URL`, optional `MATCH_GIT_BASIC_AUTHORIZATION`.
- **Build**: **`bundle exec fastlane staging_build`** → **`build/PipelineGeneric.ipa`**.
- **Optional TestFlight**: after `gym`, **`bundle exec fastlane upload_testflight_ipa`** when the orchestrator passes **`upload_to_testflight: true`** (manual **`workflow_dispatch`** with checkbox).

## Security job — `.github/workflows/ios-job-security.yml`

- **Semgrep** `p/swift` plus repo configs under **`.semgrep/`** (`mobile.yml`, `ci.yml`, `sentinel.yml` — copy this folder with the template). **TruffleHog** on repo, **Snyk** (runs only if **`SNYK_TOKEN`** is set **and** repo root has **`Package.swift`** or **`Podfile`** / **`Podfile.lock`**; otherwise skipped — avoids Snyk exit **2** on Xcode-only trees). Separate from CodeQL and from heuristic scripts in code health.

## Lint job — `.github/workflows/ios-job-lint.yml`

- **SwiftFormat** (`swiftformat --lint`, config **`.swiftformat`**) on `PipelineGeneric/PipelineGeneric`, `PipelineGeneric/PipelineGenericTests`, `PipelineGeneric/PipelineGenericUITests`, then **SwiftLint** (`--reporter github-actions-logging`) using **`.swiftlint.yml`**. Code health runs SwiftLint again for JSON + summary artifact.

## Code health — `.github/workflows/ios-code-health.yml`

- **Triggers**: `push` / `pull_request` to **`main`** and **`master`**; **`workflow_dispatch`**.
- **SwiftLint** JSON + annotations, **fail** on violations; **`.github/scripts/`** → `Reports/*.md`; artifact **`ios-code-health-reports`**.
- **Config**: **`.swiftlint.yml`** — `included:` paths under **`PipelineGeneric/`**.

## CodeQL — `.github/workflows/codeql-swift.yml`

- Push/PR to **`main`** and **`master`** + weekly **`cron`**.
- If **Autobuild** fails, use explicit **`xcodebuild`** matching **`PipelineGeneric/PipelineGeneric.xcodeproj`** and scheme **`PipelineGeneric`**.

## Dependabot — `.github/dependabot.yml`

- Weekly bumps for **`github-actions`** ecosystem at repo root (`directory: /`).

## Operations

- Bump **`XCODE_VERSION`** / **`runs-on`** together when GitHub-hosted images change; mirror across **all** workflow files that select Xcode.
- **`hashFiles(...)`** in caches should reference real paths (e.g. **`PipelineGeneric/PipelineGeneric.xcodeproj/project.pbxproj`**, **`PipelineGeneric/**/*.swift`**).

## Template reuse (another Xcode app)

When copying this repo into a **different** iOS project, replace **all** template identifiers together:

- **Project path / scheme / bundle id:** **`PipelineGeneric`**, **`PipelineGeneric/`**, **`com.codeandtheory.PipelineGeneric`**, IPA and artifact names, **`APP_BUNDLE_ID`** / **`APP_IDENTIFIER`** inputs, SwiftLint/SwiftFormat/CodeQL path lists.
- **Entry prompts:** root **`CURSOR_IOS_DEVOPS_BOOTSTRAP_PROMPT.txt`** (files already merged) or **`CURSOR_IOS_DEVOPS_APPLY_TEMPLATE_PROMPT.txt`** (copy from Pipeline-Generic + bootstrap). **Human steps:** **`SETUP_IOS_DEVOPS_KIT.md`**; **routing:** **`CURSOR_IOS_DEVOPS_REUSE.md`**.
- **Semgrep:** copy **`.semgrep/`** with workflows (see **`SETUP_IOS_DEVOPS_KIT.md`**); rules are shared unless you customize them per app.
- Keep the **DAG** unchanged unless the target app cannot run tests or needs a build-only job—then document the change in the handoff.
